  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Leanna. ?] This is the incredible-- who is now four-year-old-- [?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Jake, ?] Martin's other son.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "He is-- he's an ongoing delight and puzzlement.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he's a growing concern.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "This is-- this is my wonderful grandson, my third grandchild, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "OK, these amazingly delightful damsels are the daughters of my beautiful daughter, Shirley-- [?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Rachel ?] and [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Sarah. ?] Words cannot convey how lucky and happy and honored I feel to have had such unbelievable children like the ones sitting around me.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "On my right is Martin.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He is the oldest.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Behind me is Shirley.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And next to her is Alan David.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Alan David was 35 a month or so ago.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And Martin is at the ripe age of 40.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And Shirley's in the middle.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Shirley's a schoolteacher.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Martin works with me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And Alan is an artist.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We have kind of-- try to keep in touch growing up together.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I am sure it's been a, a, a great challenge to them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And the beat goes on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "But we've always loved each other.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And there had always been a very deep respect amongst us for one another.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I am sure that I'm not only speaking for myself when I say that every one of us appreciates who we are, and where we are, and what we are.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "It's-- it's an unbelievable, inconceivable event that I am now sitting here in 1995, after what I told you about 1944.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And, and it proves to me that trees do bear fruit and, and the good that we are for, it is possible to pursue-- not only possible, but I feel bound, as I am sure there are millions in this world, if not billions, bound to pursue that good, that common good that takes the limits off the, the, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the stops of-- of-- of going forward, of discovering, of growing, of being, of living our own days out as best as possible.",
      "word_count": 86
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK, I just want to say that I'm really grateful.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I've been the baby in the family.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I've watched the family grow and watched my father grow.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I've just developed a real reverence for life.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I'm really happy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I'm happy my father survived.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I hope that this [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] show that we're putting on, this presentation, will offer strength and courage to those who watch it and see that anything is possible.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I'm just really happy he survived and that we're all here.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we have great lives now.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I hope to pass it on to my children and them to theirs.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
